Popframe class    @{"Index" link "Classes"} @{"Super" link "AreaClass"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Popframe class is used to adjust a frame spec.

  Set Draggable to 1 to do drag and drop beetween two
  Popframe objects (using Auto in DandD()).

